# SCOUT / EDTH Munich 2026

- Challenge: 01-ats 3D Graph Exploration & Surveillance
- Only submit `src/algorithm/explorer.py` for evaluation
- `explorer.py` may only use Python stdlib + networkx
- Robot code runs on Raspberry Pi 5
- Dashboard uses Streamlit, offline only
- Mobile app / shared state is OUT OF SCOPE
- Always run `uv run run_eval.py` after algorithm changes
- Prefer minimal changes; cite file paths
